title: Ebro In The Morning - Special Guest: Hasan Minhaj
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Comedian of Hasan Minhaj sits down with Ebro in the Morning for a fun conversation about the state of politics today! 

He discusses some of the awkward moments he's encountered in recent years, what happened to his Netflix show Patriot Act, thoughts on cancel culture, and much more!

He's performing at Radio City Music Hall this weekend 2/25-2/27 for a live standup comedy show - Hashan Minhaj: The King's Jester. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
